tion and transmission of electrical power and the &amp;nbsp;effect of corona and transients on power system helped me further &amp;nbsp;understand the operations, the challenges and the entire mechanics of &amp;nbsp;the process. My analytical skills and mathematical skills assisted my &amp;nbsp;development further and saw me gaining expertise in subjects such as &amp;nbsp;Power System Analysis and topics such as Laplace and Fourier theorems. &amp;nbsp;Moving on to final year project, I got the excellent opportunity to work &amp;nbsp;under the guidance of Dr. Mira Nair. True to my passion for renewable &amp;nbsp;sources of energy, I worked on a project titled â€“ â€œReinventing the Solar &amp;nbsp;Power Satelliteâ€œ, in which I studied about the economic and functional &amp;nbsp;design of Solar Power Satellite to convert sunlight to electricity and &amp;nbsp;transfer the electricity wirelessly to various regions of Earth and also &amp;nbsp;implemented the same by means of a working model. While the project &amp;nbsp;required extensive research in the form of studying the entire process, &amp;nbsp;it also included redesigning of solar power satellite by integrating &amp;nbsp;solar arrays and microwave transmitters on opposite side of the slab &amp;nbsp;which would result in narrower beam and hence reduced size of the &amp;nbsp;rectenna and the overall system. The aim was to make solar power &amp;nbsp;satellite economically feasible and to generate maximum power at peak &amp;nbsp;hours. My work was highly applauded and appreciated.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;author-advanced&quot;&gt;My undergraduate years also saw me exploring a variety of &amp;nbsp;activities where I explored my possibilities of team work, motivation and even my ability to learn further. Evolving as a team player, I participated in Technical and Entrepreneurship festival held at Indian Institute of Technology-Kanpur, where my team-mate and I presented the prototype of an aero glider. Passionate about arts, languages and very concept of communication, I joined and underwent a 70 hours basic Spanish learning course from the most reputed Spanish learning institute in India, Instituto Hispania and topped my batch with 92.44% marks. Personally, I participated in the Delhi Half Marathons and enjoyed the exercise, the crowd and the energy the entire event exuded. I have also volunteered for the SOFTEN initiative that provides to the under-privileged, essentially professionals donating for the cause.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;author-advanced&quot;&gt;I &amp;nbsp;have now been working with Indiaâ€™s premier IT Company â€“ TCS for just &amp;nbsp;over an year. The experience has been scintillating so far and has &amp;nbsp;further helped me understand cooperates, acclimatize myself to the high &amp;nbsp;hours of work and evolve as a team player. It has also prepared me for &amp;nbsp;the rigour of another academic program for it has given me renewed &amp;nbsp;focus and motivation to do my bit. I now aspire to further my career &amp;nbsp;within the Electrical Engineering domain and work for an International &amp;nbsp;Power Generation Company. To reach the desired position and industry, I &amp;nbsp;require further training within the subject and I could fathom no better &amp;nbsp;university to provide me the same.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;author-advanced&quot;&gt;With USA being the epicenter of all major researches within the domain, I look forward to being a part of the collegeâ€™s vast community. Learning from world renowned teachers and further honing my intellect, I believe I would be able to effectively leverage my foundations in the subject and evolve further as an expert within the domain. To effectively put it, I have now laid up the circuit, connected &amp;nbsp;the wires and now I need you to complete the same, promising you that not merely would I let the circle of knowledge grow, but also light up so bright so as to illuminate the world with hope of a greener tomorrow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'I''ve revised the essay thoroughly and it looks good now.', '2016-01-19 22:16:02');

